- SORRY, THAT'S WRONG.

239
00:16:01,666 --> 00:16:03,458
IT'S CIVILIANS.  YEP.

240
00:16:03,541 --> 00:16:05,833
60% OF ALL THE GUNS
IN THE WORLD ARE OWNED

241
00:16:05,916 --> 00:16:09,166
BY ORDINARY CITIZENS.
