243
00:16:11,333 --> 00:16:13,708
AND A FRACTION TO THE POLICE.

244
00:16:13,791 --> 00:16:16,666
YOU KNOW THOSE REBEL ARMIES
THE MEDIA SALIVATES OVER?

245
00:16:16,750 --> 00:16:20,083
THEY DON'T EVEN POSSESS .1%
OF THE GUNS IN THE WORLD.

246
00:16:20,166 --> 00:16:22,791
REMEMBER WHAT YOU SAID BEFORE?

247
00:16:22,875 --> 00:16:24,958
A NORMAL PERSON WITH A GUN WILL
WIND UP DOING SOMETHING

248
00:16:25,041 --> 00:16:27,333
HE NEVER THOUGHT HIMSELF
CAPABLE OF.

249
00:16:27,416 --> 00:16:30,541
NOBODY IN THIS WORLD CAN TRULY
HOLD HIMSELF SEPARATE

250
00:16:30,625 --> 00:16:32,541
FROM VIOLENCE.

251
00:16:32,625 --> 00:16:35,625
GUNS ARE LITERALLY
WITHIN REACH OF ANYONE.

252
00:16:35,708 --> 00:16:38,291
SADLY, THAT'S WHERE
WE PUT OUR FAITH,

253
00:16:38,375 --> 00:16:41,250
IN BULLETS
RATHER THAN HUMAN KINDNESS.

254
00:16:41,333 --> 00:16:45,166
YOU KNOW, JONAH,
I REALLY DON'T WANT YOU TO DIE

255
00:16:45,250 --> 00:16:46,958
OR ANY OF THE OTHERS, OF COURSE.

256
00:16:47,041 --> 00:16:48,500
- THEN DO US ALL A FAVOR

257
00:16:48,583 --> 00:16:50,541
AND STAY AWAY
FROM ASSASSINS FROM NOW ON.

258
00:16:50,625 --> 00:16:52,916
CATS MAY HAVE NINE LIVES,
BUT I DON'T.

259
00:16:53,000 --> 00:16:57,875
- ( laughs )
SORRY, I DON'T MEAN TO LAUGH.

260
00:16:57,958 --> 00:17:01,041
YOU'RE JUST SO RIGHT.
FORGIVE ME?

261
00:17:32,208 --> 00:17:34,041
- Koko: STOP THERE.

262
00:17:35,833 --> 00:17:39,416
THE SECOND YOU AIM THAT GUN
AT ME, YOU'RE DEAD.

263
00:17:44,875 --> 00:17:47,416
- THIS GUY MUST BE BETTER
THAN THE ONE YOU USED YESTERDAY.

264
00:17:49,916 --> 00:17:54,291
I CAN'T EVEN TELL FOR SURE
WHICH DIRECTION HE'S IN.

265
00:17:54,375 --> 00:17:56,708
FINE, I YIELD.

266
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:02,041
- YOU DON'T GET IT, DO YOU?

267
00:18:02,125 --> 00:18:04,041
WHAT, YOU THINK THIS
IS SOME COURTLY DUEL?

268
00:18:04,125 --> 00:18:06,375
IT WAS ALWAYS A GAME
OF CHANCE, NOTHING MORE.

269
00:18:06,458 --> 00:18:08,125
WE'VE BEEN WAITING FOR YOU.

270
00:18:08,208 --> 00:18:11,166
